text: The 1909 Geneva Golden Tornadoes football team represented the Geneva College during the 1909 college football season. The head coach was Arthur McKean coaching the team in his third year. The team finished the season with a final record of 4–2. ==Schedule== ==References== Geneva Category:Geneva Golden Tornadoes football seasons Geneva Covenanters football
